<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Safe Template Handling</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3C1053 0%, #B51825 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #3C1053;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .success {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #3C1053;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        input[type="text"], textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #918B83;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        button {
            background: #3C1053;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        button:hover {
            background: #B51825;
        }
        .result {
            background: #F2EFEB;
            border: 2px solid #918B83;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            min-height: 100px;
        }
        .nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .nav a {
            color: #3C1053;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background: #F2EFEB;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .nav a:hover {
            background: #918B83;
            color: white;
        }
        .code-block {
            background: #302C2A;
            color: #F2EFEB;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            margin: 10px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>‚úÖ Safe Template Handling</h1>
        <div class="success">
            ‚úÖ SECURE: This endpoint properly escapes user input to prevent SSTI attacks!
        </div>
        
        <div class="nav">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/ejs">EJS</a>
            <a href="/handlebars">Handlebars</a>
            <a href="/mustache">Mustache</a>
            <a href="/nunjucks">Nunjucks</a>
            <a href="/advanced">Advanced</a>
            <a href="/safe">Safe Example</a>
        </div>

        <form method="GET">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="input">User Input (Safely Escaped):</label>
                <input type="text" id="input" name="input" value="<%= userInput %>" placeholder="Enter any input...">
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Process Input Safely</button>
        </form>

        <div class="result">
            <h3>Safe Output (HTML Escaped):</h3>
            <%= userInput %>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: #F2EFEB; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Safe Template Handling Best Practices:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Use HTML Escaping:</strong> <code>&lt;%= userInput %&gt;</code> instead of <code>&lt;%- userInput %&gt;</code></li>
                <li><strong>Validate Input:</strong> Always validate and sanitize user input before processing</li>
                <li><strong>Use Whitelist:</strong> Only allow specific template functions and variables</li>
                <li><strong>Sandbox Templates:</strong> Run templates in a sandboxed environment</li>
                <li><strong>Disable Dangerous Functions:</strong> Remove or disable dangerous global objects</li>
                <li><strong>Use Template Engines Safely:</strong> Configure template engines with security settings</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Code Example (Safe):</h4>
            <div class="code-block">
// Safe: HTML escaped output
res.render('template', { userInput: req.query.input });

// In template: &lt;%= userInput %&gt; (escaped)
            </div>
            
            <h4>Code Example (Vulnerable):</h4>
            <div class="code-block">
// Vulnerable: Unescaped output
res.render('template', { userInput: req.query.input });

// In template: &lt;%- userInput %&gt; (unescaped - DANGEROUS!)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
